<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">My first observation of your gear is that you have gone too much for charisma and are very low on hp. An enchanter has to live, either through mezz resists or charm breaks. With 2130hp you are likely to die. With only 10k to spend bazaar upgrades are not much of an option.
<br />

<br />
The first option is to go camp ornate gear. This drops from any trash in Sol Ro tower. You can easy gain access without need for pre flags.
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=3018" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=3018</a>
<br />

<br />
The efreeti is easy to kil doesnt even summon.
<br />

<br />
The other option is the omens route. Go to is harbingers spire and get the dicordant silk items. The named pop frequently, its an easy place to kill at 65, some examples.
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31588" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31588</a>
<br />
<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30699" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30699</a>
<br />

<br />
You may well get some valuable drops such as slugworms while camping. This belt is nice a quest in that zone.
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=32137" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=32137</a>
<br />

<br />
Next move to NC and camp the named. You will need the runes for you 66-68 spells, and you are working your DL faction. 
<br />

<br />
Quest back item.
<br />
<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=32065" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=32065</a>
<br />

<br />
random mob drops, but rare
<br />
<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30592" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30592</a>
<br />
also a belt cant think of name.
<br />

<br />
From named.
<br />
<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31898" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31898</a>
